name: Cat & Mouse
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
What is the project about?
CatMouseWorld build on Arbitrum,Total supply of 50,000 NFTs. 10% cats and 90% mice in a completely randomised style. 100% Creative and completely on-chain game. 

What makes your project unique?
Interesting mint experience

History of your project.
Started Apr-01-2023 10:04:31 AM +UTC

What’s next for your project?
Build a community and make more interesting games.

What can your token be used for?
Each CatMouse NFT is an independent individual with different attributes, and they can mine RICE in Barn.
